quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,aur jab hamaray farishtay ibrahim ke paas khusi ki khabar le kar aeye to kehnay lagey ke hum is bastii ke logon ko halaak kar dainay walay hain ke yahan ke rehne walay nafarman hain
  29,32,ibrahim ne kaha ke is mein to Loot bhi hain. woh kehnay lagey ke jo log yahan ( rehtay ) hain hamein sab maloom hain. hum unn ko aur unn ke ghar walon ko bchalin ge bajuz unn ki biwi ke woh peechay rehne walon mein hogi
  29,33,aur jab hamaray farishtay Loot ke paas aeye to woh unn ( ki wajah ) se nakhush aur tang dil hue. firshton ne kaha kuch khauf nah kijiyej. aur nah ranj kijiyej hum aap ko aur aap ke ghar walon ko bchalin ge magar aap ki biwi ke peechay rehne walon mein hogi
  29,34,hum is bastii ke rehne walon par is sabab se ke yeh bud-kardari karte rahay hain aasman se azaab nazil karne walay hain
  29,35,aur hum ne samajhney walay logon ke liye is bastii se aik khuli nishani chore di
  29,36,aur Mudin ki taraf unn ke bhai Shoiab ko ( bheja ) to onhon ne kaha ( ae qoum ) khuda ki ibadat karo aur pichlle din ke anay ki umeed rakho aur malik mein fasaad nah مچاؤ
  29,37,magar onhon ne unn ko jhoota samgha so unn ko zalzalay ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay
  29,38,aur Aad aur smod ko bhi ( hum ne halaak kar diya ) chunancha unn ke ( weraan ghar ) tumhari aankhon ke samnay hain aur shetan ne unn ke aamaal un ko aaraasta kar dukhaay aur un ko ( seedhay ) raste se rok diya. halaank woh dekhnay walay ( log ) they
